<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section bg-bg" id="faq">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Common questions
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Accordion -->
    <div data-animate>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Is there a real designer involved?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Yes. Every deliverable is crafted and reviewed by a senior designer. AI agents handle the research, drafting, and speed &mdash; but a human designer ensures your brand is unique, on-point, and polished.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How does the workflow actually work?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Brief &rarr; Agents research & draft &rarr; Designer refines &rarr; You review &rarr; Iterate. Tight iteration is built into the model &mdash; agents make revisions fast, so you're never waiting weeks for a simple change.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How fast are deliverables?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Most projects are delivered in 1&ndash;2 weeks. Because AI agents handle the heavy lifting (research, variations, asset generation), your designer can focus on quality and refinement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Will AI output look generic?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">No. AI handles research and speed; the human designer ensures uniqueness and creative direction. Think of the agents as a research team, not the creative director. Your brand will be custom-crafted, not template-generated.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Who owns the designs?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">You do, 100%. All intellectual property is transferred to you upon delivery. Full design files, brand guidelines, and source assets are all yours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Is my data safe?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p class="pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Yes. All work is confidential and secure. We don't train on your data, share it, or use it beyond your project. Your startup's information stays between us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
